[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "ただいま戻りました。\n無数島群域西部の調査を終えてきました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "おかえりなさい、リンカ。\n早速だけど、現地の様子を報告してくれる？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "はい。新たに開通した海路は順調です。島々の住民も、\nランターナの人々の出入りには慣れてきたようでした",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そう……私たち異邦人の行動範囲も広がったわけね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "はい。今後は、より広域の情報整理が必要になるかと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "まったく、今までランターナ王国内だけで\n手一杯だったのに、無数島群域まで加わるなんて……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "報告書の山が減る気がしないわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "ぼやいてる暇があったら手を動かしなさい。\nそんなことしたって仕事は減らないんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "本当に助かってるわ、クーデリアちゃん。\nあなたが来てくれてから、仕事が倍速で進むもの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "しかし、クーデリアは貴族だと聞きました。\nなぜこのような仕事に慣れているのでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "貴族かどうかなんて関係ないわよ。\nできる人はできる、それだけのことじゃない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "ただいま戻りました！　マリオンさん、\n調べてきたことを報告します",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "おかえりなさい、フィリスちゃん。\n今回はどこを回ってきたの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "えっと……レスナちゃんたちが行ったっていう\nオーベンランドまで！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "ちょっと待って、それって前回の報告とぜんぜん\n違う場所じゃない！　まさか、そんな大移動を……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "はい。人々の最北の到達点……\nどんな場所か気になって、つい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "フィリスの行動力には驚かされます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "はあ……こうして報告を受けているだけだと、\nみんなが今どこに居るのか、掴みづらいのよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "ほんとよ。みんな好き勝手に動き回ってるんだもの。\n受け取った情報の整理だけじゃ追いつかないわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "常に全員の位置を把握できる方法があれば、\nもっと効率的なんだけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "うーん……\n何かいい方法、ないかなあ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "地図にみんながいる場所の印を付けてくれる\n道具でもあれば、楽になりそうですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "なに言ってるの……って思ったけど、\nもし本当にできるのなら悪くないわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クーデリア",
		"romanized_name": "Cuderia ",
		"model_path_hash": "5065022776013089089",
		"text": "錬金術士たちが力を合わせれば、\nもしかしてもしかするかもしれないわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7389579890239046457",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "フィリス",
		"romanized_name": "Firis",
		"model_path_hash": "872339722236451917",
		"text": "わたしも協力するよ！　\nみんなの居場所が分かれば、もっと安心できるもん",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1330857698433587221",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そうね、みんなの力を合わせて、\nもっといい管理方法を考えましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]